<title>UK: Merrill sets calls on Portugal Telecom.</title>
<headline>Merrill sets calls on Portugal Telecom.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-07-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Merrill Lynch International said it has issued 10 million American-style call warrants, on Portugal Telecom.</p>
<p>One share is controlled by 10 warrants.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    8,000 PTE		 PREMIUM	14.39 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE     86.49 PTE		 GEARING	8.96 X</p>
<p> EXPIRATION	31.JUL.98		 PAYDATE	24.JUL.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   LONDON		    MIN EXER LOT 1,000</p>
<p>SPOT REFERENCE  7,750 PTE</p>
